 bình nhạc - Ức Ngô giang thưởng mộc tê - 清平樂－憶吳江賞木樨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-c%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-03/poem-qX3DrKjvx5rLrg7u9rL4Ww">Thưởng cúc kỳ 03 - 賞菊其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-Quang/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Can-h%C3%A0nh/poem-NW7ORv6C9SWGTZSpVOXHMw">Trường Can hành - 長干行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-Quang/author-Fb9iKQ84kPvMS5KYYIAOWQ">Lý Hiếu Quang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/%E1%BB%A8c-Trung-d%C5%A9ng-Thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%C3%B3-%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-T%C3%B4n-%C4%90%C3%A0i-h%E1%BB%93i-thi-tr%C3%ACnh-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-PqSwvT4-WTN5Y1giD7HeKg">Ức Trung dũng Thiếu phó Đặng Tôn Đài, hồi thi trình thướng kỳ 2 - 憶中勇少傅鄧尊台，回詩呈上其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/author-pEICBCCrXfpItm0RL1cOfw">Đinh Nho Hoàn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
